  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A literature-based survey of published hemolysis data was conducted to characterise model performance across operating conditions; the survey synthesised findings from twelve peer-reviewed studies covering comparable pump geometries and flow regimes. This evidence is presented as the primary validation basis supporting the credibility determination.",
