        "name": "Literature review of CFD hemolysis studies for centrifugal blood pumps",
        "description": "Systematic review of peer-reviewed publications (2010–2024) reporting CFD-based hemolysis predictions for centrifugal blood pumps. Twelve studies meeting inclusion criteria were identified; data on model form, mesh resolution, turbulence closure, and reported hemolysis errors were extracted and tabulated. No new experimental measurements were conducted.",
        "activityType": "literature-review",
